; ◈.design-principles (FULL ENFORCEMENT)
; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@design-principles⟿ SOLID ⫶ GRASP ⫶ DRY ⫶ KISS ⫶ YAGNI ⫶ YSH

; SOLID
SRP⟿ one.responsibility.per.unit
OCP⟿ open.extend ⫶ closed.modify
LSP⟿ subtypes.substitutable
ISP⟿ specific.interfaces ⫶ ¬fat
DIP⟿ depend.abstractions ⫶ ¬concretions

; GRASP
creator⟿ who.has.data.creates
information-expert⟿ who.knows.does
low-coupling⟿ minimize.dependencies
high-cohesion⟿ focused.responsibilities
controller⟿ coordinate.use-cases
polymorphism⟿ vary.by.type
pure-fabrication⟿ artificial.for.design
indirection⟿ decouple.via.intermediate
protected-variations⟿ stable.interfaces

; DRY + KISS + YAGNI + YSH
DRY⟿ single.source.of.truth ⫶ rule.of.three
KISS⟿ simplest.solution.that.works
YAGNI⟿ ¬build.until.needed
YSH⟿ pattern.3x.proven⟿ abstract.NOW

; YSH = You Should Have (dialectical inverse of YAGNI)
; When pattern proven 3+ times → abstract NOW, don't wait

